---
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';
import { readFileSync } from 'fs';
import yaml from 'yaml';
import aboutImg from '../assets/portraits/img-3822.webp';
import aboutImgTeaser from '../assets/portraits/romain-dal-farra-realisateur-tournage.webp';

interface Props {
  variant?: 'teaser' | 'full';
  showHeader?: boolean;
}

const { variant = 'full', showHeader = true } = Astro.props;
const aboutData = yaml.parse(readFileSync('src/data/about.yaml', 'utf-8'));
const isTeaser = variant === 'teaser';
---

<section class="about section" id="a-propos" aria-label="À propos">
  <div class="section__container">
    <div class="about__grid">
      <div class="wipe-reveal">
        <div class="about__portrait">
          <Image src={isTeaser ? aboutImgTeaser : aboutImg} alt="Romain Dal Farra — portrait" class="about__portrait-img" width={600} height={800} loading="lazy" />
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="about__text reveal-right">
        {showHeader && <span class="section__label">À propos</span>}
        {showHeader && !isTeaser && (
          <>
            <h2 class="section__heading">Romain Dal Farra</h2>
            <div class="section__divider"></div>
          </>
        )}

        {isTeaser ? (
          <>
            <p>Je développe une approche visuelle centrée sur la lumière, la composition et le rythme de l'image. Chaque projet est pour moi l'occasion de traduire des émotions en langage visuel, en construisant des cadres qui racontent autant qu'ils montrent. J'explore les contrastes, les textures et les mouvements pour donner du relief aux récits.</p>
            <blockquote class="about__quote">
              « La lumière ne montre pas seulement ce qui est visible, elle révèle ce que l'on ressent. »
            </blockquote>
          </>
        ) : (
          <>
            <p>{aboutData.bio_intro}</p>
            <blockquote class="about__quote">
              « {aboutData.citation} »
            </blockquote>
            <p>{aboutData.bio_parcours}</p>
            <p>{aboutData.bio_expertise}</p>
            <p>{aboutData.bio_transmission}</p>
          </>
        )}
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .about {
    background:
      radial-gradient(ellipse 80% 50% at 10% 50%, rgba(212, 160, 74, 0.03) 0%, transparent 70%),
      linear-gradient(180deg, var(--black-deep) 0%, #0f0f0f 30%, #121210 50%, #0f0f0f 70%, var(--black-deep) 100%);
  }
  .about__grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 4rem;
    align-items: center;
  }
  .about__portrait {
    position: relative;
    aspect-ratio: 3 / 4;
    -webkit-mask-image: radial-gradient(ellipse 70% 60% at 45% 40%, black 20%, transparent 72%);
    mask-image: radial-gradient(ellipse 70% 60% at 45% 40%, black 20%, transparent 72%);
  }
  .about__portrait-img {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    width: 100%; height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    object-position: 35% center;
    filter: grayscale(1) contrast(1.1);
    transition: transform 1.2s var(--ease-cinematic), filter 0.6s var(--ease-smooth);
  }
  .about__portrait:hover .about__portrait-img {
    transform: scale(1.04);
    filter: grayscale(1) contrast(1.15) brightness(1.05);
  }
  .about__text p {
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
    color: var(--gray-lighter);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
  }
  .about__text p:first-of-type::first-line { color: var(--white); }
  .about__quote {
    border-left: 2px solid var(--amber-dim);
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
    margin: 2rem 0;
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--gray-light);
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .about__grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 2.5rem; }
    .about__portrait { max-width: 280px; margin: 0 auto; }
  }
</style>
